text: Selena Charteris (born 5 June 1981) is a New Zealand cricketer. She played in five Women's One Day International cricket (WODI) matches and two Women's Twenty20 International cricket (WT20I) matches in 2007. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand women cricketers Category:New Zealand women One Day International cricketers Category:New Zealand women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Cricketers from Timaru
